It seems I've searched the interwebs for hours without any results. Is there ANY payment processing I could use?<p>- Google checkout: US (and UK?!) only;
- Amazon payment: US only;
- Stripe: US only (nooooo!).<p>I want payment for something very experimental, so I don't want to incorporate beforehand (In other words, the payment processing company should accept ME as an individual).<p>As a last resort there's always Paypal, but I would very much like to use something else.<p>I must say, this is making me want to have a bitcoin-like solution.<p>Thanks in advance!
